## Rules (violating = bugs)
  [ios] touchend + click both fire on iOS — use handling flag with 300ms timeout
  [ios] Audio.play() blocked until user gesture — never autoplay, init on first tap
  [ios] Safari blocks Audio context creation outside user gesture — wrap in click/touchstart handler
  [ios] history.back() unreliable in SPA-like setup — use direct window.location.href
  [cloudflare] Workers have 10ms CPU limit (free) / 50ms (paid) — no heavy computation server-side
  [cloudflare] D1 is SQLite — no ALTER COLUMN, no concurrent writes, 1MB response limit
  [cloudflare] Static assets in public/ copied to dist/ by Vite — changes need rebuild
  [i18n] All 3 languages (EN/ZH/TH) required in every NW_I18N.register call
  [i18n] data-i18n uses textContent (strips HTML) — use data-i18n-html for content with tags
  [i18n] NW_I18N.onChange callback fires AFTER core applies textContent — use setTimeout(0) to override with innerHTML
  [i18n] nw_lang localStorage key — never use a different key for language storage
  [i18n] Never generate [ZH]/[TH] placeholder prefixes — use English fallback directly. Prefixes are visible to users and look broken.
  [battle] Mobile viewport must handle 320-375px — test at minimum 320px
  [battle] Card hand must use flex-wrap or scroll — overflow:hidden clips cards on mobile
  [battle] Battle must always give rewards — never zero. Even a loss gives 10 Gold consolation.
  [battle] nw-battle-coach.js must load AFTER nw-battle-v7.js — it hooks into DOM elements created by battle init
  [battle] nw-battle-assist.js must load AFTER nw-battle-v7.js; it reads window.NW_BATTLE API which is set at IIFE end
  [battle] Assist skips all visuals when coach overlay is active (coachActive() checks for #coachOverlay)
